    "SUMMARY": "Stadio Mario Rigamonti is a football stadium located in Brescia, Italy. It is currently the home of Brescia Calcio.\nIt is dedicated to Mario Rigamonti, a defender of the Grande Torino, born in Brescia, who died in the Superga air disaster in May 1949."
